Bot_v2_Groq_AI_Analysze_Decision
Project Diagram
Version: v2.0.0

======================================================================
1) PROJECT PURPOSE
======================================================================
This repository is a production-oriented staged trading decision system
focused on:

- deterministic candidate generation
- candidate normalization / alias-aware deduplication
- Groq-based AI decision confirmation
- authoritative AI decision contract via models/schemas.py
- bootstrap-safe integration path
- no full execution runtime loop yet in app/main.py

The repo currently supports:
- foundation/bootstrap startup
- candidate finalization boundary
- Groq adapter layer
- candidate-to-groq integration smoke test
- optional gated smoke path through app/main.py

