3) AUTHORITATIVE DECISION CONTRACT
======================================================================
models/schemas.py :: AIDecision is the authoritative AI decision contract.

Groq output must be adapted into AIDecision.

Important AIDecision fields:
- candidate_id
- decision
- approved
- confidence
- entry_min
- entry_max
- stop_loss
- setup_quality
- trend_alignment
- regime_fit
- exhaustion_risk
- reason
- model_name
- prompt_version
- latency_ms
- valid_response

Important rule:
- Do not silently change this contract
- Parser must map model output into this schema
- Fail closed on malformed responses

