4) CURRENT FUNCTIONAL FLOW
======================================================================
A) Bootstrap path
----------------------------------------------------------------------
app/main.py
  -> load config
  -> validate config
  -> initialize storage
  -> print runtime summary
  -> normal bootstrap success

B) Candidate path
----------------------------------------------------------------------
raw market/candidate rows
  -> candidate_engine.py
  -> decision_validator.py
  -> candidate_pipeline_postprocessor.py
  -> candidate_scan_finalize.py
  -> finalized output:
       accepted / rejected / all_items / log_lines / summary

C) Groq adapter path
----------------------------------------------------------------------
accepted candidate
  -> groq_prompt_builder.py
  -> groq_client.py
  -> groq_response_parser.py
  -> AIDecision

D) Gated integration path through main.py
----------------------------------------------------------------------
app/main.py
  -> normal bootstrap
  -> if RUN_CANDIDATE_TO_GROQ_SMOKE=1:
       from app.smoke_test_candidate_to_groq import run_integration_test
       run_integration_test()
  -> print foundation success line

