8) SAFE OPERATION MODES
======================================================================
Mode 1: Normal bootstrap
----------------------------------------------------------------------
python app/main.py

Behavior:
- config load
- storage init
- runtime summary
- no Groq integration smoke path executed

Mode 2: Gated candidate-to-groq smoke path
----------------------------------------------------------------------
PowerShell:
$env:RUN_CANDIDATE_TO_GROQ_SMOKE="1"
python app/main.py

Behavior:
- bootstrap path runs
- candidate-to-groq smoke path runs
- Groq live path runs only if GROQ_API_KEY is configured

Mode 3: Direct integration smoke test
----------------------------------------------------------------------
python app/smoke_test_candidate_to_groq.py

Behavior:
- finalization + Groq integration test only

